What's new in BudgeTrak:
• Ads upgraded from banner to native — richer card-style format that pays better, with no letterboxing
• Tablets and large phones see a bigger ad with an embedded image or muted video; small phones see a compact single-row card
• Video ads start muted, show a clear mute/unmute icon, and re-mute automatically when you return to the app
• Visible "Ad" label on every ad per industry policy
• Security and stability fixes
